original: Elmsjö, Rut Ingeborg, tandläkare, Ulricehamn, f. 22/3/97 i N. Solberga, Jönköp. 1. — Stud:ex. v. Palmgr. samsk. i Sthlm 22, med. kand. v. Ka-rol. inst. i Sthlm 29, tandl. 31. Vik. i Vetlanda 31, prakt, i Ulricehamn sed. 32, även skoltandl. där.
translated: Elmsjö, Rut Ingeborg, dentist, Ulricehamn, b. March 22, 1897 in N. Solberga, Jönköping. Graduated from Palmgrenska samrealskolan in Stockholm in 1922 and earned a Bachelor of Medicine from the Karolinska Institute in Stockholm in 1929. Became a dentist in 1931. Worked as a temporary dentist in Vetlanda in 1931 and opened a dental practice in Ulricehamn in 1932. Also worked as a school dentist there.
